              ],
              "free_text": [
                " A cylindrical plastic scintillator 64mm in",
                "diam. and 100 mm in height coupled to a K14FS50",
                "photomultiplier tube."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "BF3"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Measurements were monitored both by a",
                "stilbene scin.counter with a high-energy threshold",
